name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Because this? It may be Fox, but it isn’t news.

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Where are the reasonable voices on the right?

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: We don’t have to agree on everything, but come on! If that was a group of trans-swimmers shooting a guy for making a cell phone video, you’d be heating up the electric chairs right now. Admit it.

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: The man Stephen Miller referred to as a ‘would-be assassin,’ Alex Pretti, was an ICU nurse who treated veterans, which is about as patriotic as it gets,

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Alex Pretti, may he rest in peace.
